Press Meetup";s:10:"meetup_url";s:46:"https://www.meetup.com/tokyo-wordpress-meetup/";s:4:"date";s:19:"2026-07-09 18:30:00";s:8:"end_date";s:19:"2026-07-09 21:00:00";s:20:"start_unix_timestamp";i:1783589400;s:18:"end_unix_timestamp";i:1783598400;s:8:"location";a:4:{s:8:"location";s:20:"Shinjuku City, Japan";s:7:"country";s:2:"jp";s:8:"latitude";d:35.69429;s:9:"longitude";d:139.69585;}}i:4;a:10:{s:4:"type";s:6:"meetup";s:5:"title";s:82:"平日午前のOnline WordPress Meetup by Chiba WordPress Meetup　26年7月の会";s:3:"url";s:63:"https://www.meetup.com/chiba-wordpress-meetup/events/315337769/";s:6:"meetup";s:22:"Chiba WordPress Meetup";s:10:"meetup_url";s:46:"https://www.meetup.com/chiba-wordpress-meetup/";s:4:"date";s:19:"2026-07-10 10:00:00";s:8:"end_date";s:19:"2026-07-10 12:00:00";s:20:"start_unix_timestamp";i:1783645200;s:18:"end_unix_timestamp";i:1783652400;s:8:"location";a:4:{s:8:"location";s:6:"Online";s:7:"country";s:2:"JP";s:8:"latitude";d:35.61;s:9:"longitude";d:140.11;}}i:5;a:10:{s:4:"type";s:6:"meetup";s:5:"title";s:140:"【横浜】参加無料！初心者からプロまで歓迎！WordPress好きが集う勉強会＆交流会 / Yokohama WordPress Meetup #44";s:3:"url";s:66:"https://www.meetup.com/kanagawa-wordpress-meetup/events/315309102/";s:6:"meetup";s:25:"Kanagawa WordPress Meetup";s:10:"meetup_url";s:49:"https://www.meetup.com/kanagawa-wordpress-meetup/";s:4:"date";s:19:"2026-07-12 14:00:00";s:8:"end_date";s:19:"2026-07-12 17:00:00";s:20:"start_unix_timestamp";i:1783832400;s:18:"end_unix_timestamp";i:1783843200;s:8:"location";a:4:{s:8:"location";s:15:"Yokohama, Japan";s:7:"country";s:2:"jp";s:8:"latitude";d:35.468464;s:9:"longitude";d:139.62071;}}}}', 'off');
